128
00:07:00,291 --> 00:07:01,641
Are you feeling better now?

129
00:07:03,291 --> 00:07:05,040
Will you accomplish the assignment?

130
00:07:06,130 --> 00:07:07,120
I will.

131
00:07:08,570 --> 00:07:09,401
Very well.

132
00:07:10,370 --> 00:07:12,120
