133
00:07:14,010 --> 00:07:16,201
Why do you lock the door
when you sleep?

134
00:07:18,771 --> 00:07:21,800
My phone is synced
with your exercise record.

135
00:07:21,891 --> 00:07:23,249
It woke me up
in the middle of the night.

136
00:07:23,250 --> 00:07:25,360
