146
00:07:46,810 --> 00:07:48,360
I couldn't move you.

147
00:07:49,091 --> 00:07:50,360
My bad.

148
00:07:51,091 --> 00:07:53,210
I'll look after you

149
00:07:53,211 --> 00:07:54,360
