and give you sunshine.

155
00:08:04,130 --> 00:08:05,920
You can't even take care of the cactus.

156
00:08:06,451 --> 00:08:08,240
But I can take good care of you.

157
00:08:09,010 --> 00:08:10,009
With me around,

158
00:08:10,010 --> 00:08:12,081
