184
00:09:53,171 --> 00:09:54,440
sheltered?

185
00:09:57,290 --> 00:09:58,601
You don't have to answer me.

186
00:09:59,250 --> 00:10:00,680
Let me tell you.

187
00:10:02,410 --> 00:10:04,361
I'm the opposite of those words.

188
00:10:05,571 --> 00:10:07,200
I hate crowds.

189
00:10:07,971 --> 00:10:10,001
Noisy occasions

190
00:10:10,211 --> 00:10:11,800
