196
00:10:27,250 --> 00:10:28,761
I've resigned. I'm jobless.

197
00:10:29,451 --> 00:10:31,401
I leech off my parents.

198
00:10:33,010 --> 00:10:34,601
I'm also seeing a therapist.

199
00:10:36,051 --> 00:10:37,721
I was told

200
00:10:37,811 --> 00:10:39,521
