do you really think she'd fall for it?

283
00:18:55,810 --> 00:18:57,880
The Demoness ignored him.

284
00:18:57,891 --> 00:19:00,089
But somehow, her ex managed

285
00:19:00,090 --> 00:19:01,970
to make Roger return

286
00:19:01,971 --> 00:19:03,201
on a red-eye flight.

287
00:19:03,250 --> 00:19:05,241
That's why
the Demoness couldn't avoid it.

288
00:19:05,330 --> 00:19:06,921
They're discussing it
in the meeting room now.

289
00:19:06,931 --> 00:19:08,001
Wait.

290
00:19:08,371 --> 00:19:09,569
What does any of this

291
00:19:09,570 --> 00:19:11,130
have to do

292
00:19:11,131 --> 00:19:12,521
with the selection?

293
00:19:12,651 --> 00:19:13,890
It's all because

294
00:19:13,891 --> 00:19:15,489
of this sudden change.

295
00:19:15,490 --> 00:19:18,730
The meeting room was scheduled
for next Friday to fit Roger's time.

296
00:19:18,731 --> 00:19:19,809
Now that he's returned earlier,

297
00:19:19,810 --> 00:19:21,800
we should stick with his schedule.

298
00:19:37,050 --> 00:19:38,961
I understand what you're saying,
Mr. Huang.

299
00:19:39,171 --> 00:19:40,769
However, the investment

300
00:19:40,770 --> 00:19:42,241
isn't under my charge.

301
00:19:42,411 --> 00:19:44,161
Please excuse me.

302
00:19:46,371 --> 00:19:48,400
Please stay, Ms. Zhang.

303
00:19:51,770 --> 00:19:52,880
Here's the thing.

304
00:19:53,090 --> 00:19:55,761
Even though Ms. Zhang is not in charge
of the investment, she manages the business.

305
00:19:55,810 --> 00:19:57,730
I need her help to tell me

306
00:19:57,731 --> 00:19:59,840
what suitable projects we can discuss.

307
00:20:03,810 --> 00:20:05,080
Ms. Zhang,

308
00:20:05,731 --> 00:20:08,040
since Mr. Huang wants you to stay,

309
00:20:08,611 --> 00:20:09,560
well,

310
00:20:09,931 --> 00:20:11,761
please do us a favor
and stay for a while more.

311
00:20:21,090 --> 00:20:22,009
Mr. Huang,

312
00:20:22,010 --> 00:20:23,241
well,

313
00:20:23,330 --> 00:20:25,481
shall we?

314
00:20:25,891 --> 00:20:27,080
Of course.

315
00:20:30,451 --> 00:20:31,690
Some parts are lacking.

316
00:20:31,691 --> 00:20:33,489
I've already highlighted them.

317
00:20:33,490 --> 00:20:34,721
Review it as quickly as possible

318
00:20:34,770 --> 00:20:36,441
and send it back by the end of the day.

319
00:20:37,490 --> 00:20:38,921
Thank you.

320
00:20:38,931 --> 00:20:40,890
I'd prefer the supplement
as a thank-you.

321
00:20:40,891 --> 00:20:41,880
Get moving.

322
00:20:47,850 --> 00:20:48,961
No need.

323
00:20:50,611 --> 00:20:51,800
Jacqueline,

324
00:20:52,530 --> 00:20:53,640
as for the next theme

325
00:20:54,050 --> 00:20:56,450
on the virtual idol holographic concert,

326
00:20:56,451 --> 00:20:58,281
I promised to bring
Guan Xingxin with me.

327
00:20:58,451 --> 00:21:00,681
Now that she has left Nextmonday,

328
00:21:01,850 --> 00:21:03,481
I came here to check with you

329
00:21:03,770 --> 00:21:04,890
how much impact this interview

330
00:21:04,891 --> 00:21:06,521
might have on us.

331
00:21:06,691 --> 00:21:07,809
Your contract

332
00:21:07,810 --> 00:21:10,880
didn't include maintaining
Nextmonday's reputation.

333
00:21:11,611 --> 00:21:13,241
Before this, I was only
helping one person.

334
00:21:13,290 --> 00:21:14,681
But now, I have a team.

335
00:21:15,090 --> 00:21:17,201
It'll be bad for everyone if this messes up.

336
00:21:17,290 --> 00:21:19,001
I'm doing this for your benefit.

337
00:21:20,290 --> 00:21:22,009
Someone once told me

338
00:21:22,010 --> 00:21:23,370
that things of no value

339
00:21:23,371 --> 00:21:24,809
should be thrown away immediately,

340
00:21:24,810 --> 00:21:26,721
including relationships and emotions.

341
00:21:27,090 --> 00:21:30,360
Layla's comeback will surely turn the tables
in terms of her public acceptance.

342
00:21:30,891 --> 00:21:32,721
It's not a bad thing
to have controversies.

343
00:21:32,770 --> 00:21:34,080
Reputations can rise higher

344
00:21:34,451 --> 00:21:36,120
unless they hit rock bottom.

345
00:21:38,850 --> 00:21:39,489
Understood.

346
00:21:39,490 --> 00:21:40,681
I'll play it by ear.

347
00:21:41,211 --> 00:21:42,080
Hold on.

348
00:21:42,731 --> 00:21:44,730
Gu Yi isn't familiar
with things like this.

349
00:21:44,731 --> 00:21:46,001
Get it outsourced.

350
00:21:47,691 --> 00:21:49,281
Do you have any candidates?

351
00:21:52,361 --> 00:21:53,823
(Huang Wenda)

352
00:22:05,530 --> 00:22:06,769
Wipe your mouth.

353
00:22:06,770 --> 00:22:08,400
All right.

354
00:23:13,971 --> 00:23:16,080
I've heard from Jacqueline

355
00:23:16,090 --> 00:23:17,761
that you're good at maintaining clients.

356
00:23:18,611 --> 00:23:21,481
I didn't believe it at first.

357
00:23:22,290 --> 00:23:24,400
But after today's event,

358
00:23:24,971 --> 00:23:27,040
I think you're smart.

359
00:23:29,490 --> 00:23:31,040
Smart people

360
00:23:31,611 --> 00:23:33,880
should be placed in smarter roles.

361
00:23:36,171 --> 00:23:38,040
The head of the supplement,

362
00:23:40,330 --> 00:23:41,360
do you like it?

363
00:24:08,010 --> 00:24:09,489
(Qingya, happy birthday)
That's it?

364
00:24:09,490 --> 00:24:11,730
Your junior is so ungenerous.

365
00:24:11,731 --> 00:24:13,560
Only a piece of paper
for your birthday present?

366
00:24:14,050 --> 00:24:15,569
She likes it.

367
00:24:15,570 --> 00:24:17,761
She's making a man out of him.

368
00:24:23,371 --> 00:24:24,921
Ms. Zhang, you asked for me?

369
00:24:25,171 --> 00:24:26,840
Ask Liang Daiwen to come up.

370
00:24:27,770 --> 00:24:28,880
Oh, right, Ms. Zhang.

371
00:24:29,010 --> 00:24:31,089
HF Design Company's admin sent a message

372
00:24:31,090 --> 00:24:33,840
asking if you need to increase the budget
for the annual dinner's prizes.

373
00:24:35,371 --> 00:24:36,721
Is Liang Daiwen going?

374
00:24:36,850 --> 00:24:37,569
If so,

375
00:24:37,570 --> 00:24:39,040
add ten more flagship phones.

376
00:24:39,451 --> 00:24:40,650
His graphic tablet is old.

377
00:24:40,651 --> 00:24:41,800
Get him a new one.

378
00:24:42,490 --> 00:24:44,600
Is that included in the budget?

379
00:24:45,691 --> 00:24:46,690
No, use my individual account.

380
00:24:46,691 --> 00:24:47,761
Get the best tablet.

381
00:24:48,530 --> 00:24:49,521
Understood.

382
00:25:07,770 --> 00:25:09,560
This is a newly drafted contact.

383
00:25:09,891 --> 00:25:12,040
Review it and see if
there's anything missing.

384
00:25:18,731 --> 00:25:19,890
Take a look.

385
00:25:19,891 --> 00:25:21,521
I may have missed out on something.

386
00:25:23,290 --> 00:25:24,281
Qingya,

387
00:25:25,770 --> 00:25:27,161
I want to resign.

388
00:25:28,891 --> 00:25:30,281
What do you mean?

389
00:25:31,250 --> 00:25:32,761
The term is up.

390
00:25:33,931 --> 00:25:35,961
I want to do something I truly want.

391
00:25:39,931 --> 00:25:41,400
And what is it that you want to do?

392
00:25:42,171 --> 00:25:43,880
Accessibility design again?

393
00:25:44,211 --> 00:25:45,730
Is it because I've given you
the best offer,

394
00:25:45,731 --> 00:25:47,640
and you're making money too easily?

395
00:25:47,691 --> 00:25:50,320
Is your gratitude for me
and our relationship only worth five years?

396
00:25:50,611 --> 00:25:51,690
The moment the term is up,

397
00:25:51,691 --> 00:25:53,761
you leave to do charity work
for disabled people?

398
00:25:54,490 --> 00:25:57,600
I don't think HF Design Company ever
lacks new designers who serve wealthy clients.

399
00:25:59,290 --> 00:26:00,130
Liang Daiwen,

400
00:26:00,131 --> 00:26:01,880
think this through.

401
00:26:04,131 --> 00:26:05,600
I've already given it a serious thought.

402
00:26:05,850 --> 00:26:07,360
Have you made up your mind?

403
00:26:09,131 --> 00:26:10,360
Yes, I have.

404
00:26:14,731 --> 00:26:17,320
I know you won't be easily swayed
once you make a decision.

405
00:26:17,810 --> 00:26:19,080
I won't force you either.

406
00:26:19,451 --> 00:26:21,560
But you should give me some time.

407
00:26:22,211 --> 00:26:23,049
At least allow me

408
00:26:23,050 --> 00:26:24,840
to find someone to replace you.

409
00:26:25,611 --> 00:26:27,360
There are new designers
who need opportunities.

410
00:26:28,931 --> 00:26:30,921
I'll tie up all loose ends
before I leave.

411
00:26:36,891 --> 00:26:38,001
All right.

412
00:26:39,211 --> 00:26:40,560
There's a client

413
00:26:40,570 --> 00:26:42,849
who specifically requested
the best designer I have.

414
00:26:42,850 --> 00:26:45,800
There's no one more suitable than you.
Please do me this favor.

415
00:26:46,651 --> 00:26:48,009
Complete this draft,

416
00:26:48,010 --> 00:26:49,201
and I'll let you go.

417
00:26:54,411 --> 00:26:55,320
Okay.

418
00:27:20,250 --> 00:27:21,690
Come on

419
00:27:21,691 --> 00:27:23,049
and have a look.

420
00:27:23,050 --> 00:27:25,769
(Gu Yi: Mr. Liang, I'll be working late tonight.)
You don't want to miss the best deal.

421
00:27:25,770 --> 00:27:26,839
(Liang Daiwen: OK.)
Christmas Eve

422
00:27:26,840 --> 00:27:28,521
(Gu Yi: Merry Christmas Eve.)
with peace apples.

423
00:27:28,570 --> 00:27:31,320
(Eat an apple for me.)
May your family be happy and lucky.

424
00:27:31,891 --> 00:27:33,040
Handsome,

425
00:27:33,171 --> 00:27:34,400
it's Christmas Eve.

426
00:27:34,490 --> 00:27:36,489
Buy a peace apple
for your girlfriend.

427
00:27:36,490 --> 00:27:37,210
Look at them.

428
00:27:37,211 --> 00:27:38,690
My apples

429
00:27:38,691 --> 00:27:40,080
are fresh

430
00:27:40,171 --> 00:27:41,521
and red.

431
00:27:42,691 --> 00:27:43,769
How much is it?

432
00:27:43,770 --> 00:27:44,730
Thirty.

433
00:27:44,731 --> 00:27:45,650
They just arrived today.

434
00:27:45,651 --> 00:27:47,610
Look at them. They are fresh.

435
00:27:47,611 --> 00:27:48,640
Over here.

436
00:27:48,991 --> 00:27:51,130
(Shen Zhimin)

437
00:27:51,131 --> 00:27:52,410
We're selling at a fair price,

438
00:27:52,411 --> 00:27:53,249
you know?

439
00:27:53,250 --> 00:27:55,761
Hello? Is this Price Bureau?

440
00:27:56,090 --> 00:27:57,521
Hey, don't.

441
00:27:58,010 --> 00:27:59,610
Well, you don't have to do that.

442
00:27:59,611 --> 00:28:00,089
Right?

443
00:28:00,090 --> 00:28:01,560
How much is this?

444
00:28:02,090 --> 00:28:03,441
Fifteen.

445
00:28:03,451 --> 00:28:05,281
Fifteen, is that okay?

446
00:28:05,411 --> 00:28:06,489
I'll take one.

447
00:28:06,490 --> 00:28:07,640
Sure.

448
00:28:07,850 --> 00:28:10,721
You see, the business is tough.

449
00:28:10,971 --> 00:28:12,089
So tough.

450
00:28:12,090 --> 00:28:13,001
Jeez.

451
00:29:00,090 --> 00:29:01,640
I can't even ride back.

452
00:29:02,290 --> 00:29:03,840
Tough luck.

453
00:29:06,050 --> 00:29:07,450
Why are you back?

454
00:29:07,451 --> 00:29:08,880
It's raining outside.

455
00:29:09,131 --> 00:29:10,130
I came to get the umbrella.

456
00:29:10,131 --> 00:29:10,849
Did you get wet?

457
00:29:10,850 --> 00:29:11,809
Here are some tissues.

458
00:29:11,810 --> 00:29:12,961
Here.

459
00:29:14,770 --> 00:29:16,049
Are you not leaving yet?

460
00:29:16,050 --> 00:29:17,721
I'm not done yet.

461
00:29:19,131 --> 00:29:20,961
Today's Christmas.

462
00:29:21,330 --> 00:29:23,080
Do give the Santa face.

463
00:29:23,891 --> 00:29:27,289
If the Santa can
give me a quick promotion,

464
00:29:27,290 --> 00:29:28,681
I'll get off work right away.

465
00:29:31,611 --> 00:29:32,560
All right.

466
00:29:33,090 --> 00:29:34,201
It's saved.

467
00:29:36,691 --> 00:29:37,840
Why?

468
00:29:37,891 --> 00:29:39,370
Everyone has left to celebrate.

469
00:29:39,371 --> 00:29:40,921
No one will spread rumors about us.

470
00:29:41,411 --> 00:29:42,400
Let's go

471
00:29:42,570 --> 00:29:44,281
grab something hot.

472
00:29:44,651 --> 00:29:44,930
I...

473
00:29:44,931 --> 00:29:46,120
It's on me.

474
00:29:46,451 --> 00:29:47,249
- Okay.
- Do it later.

475
00:29:47,250 --> 00:29:48,049
Okay.

476
00:29:48,050 --> 00:29:49,249
Stop pushing the chair.

477
00:29:49,250 --> 00:29:50,600
You can do it later.

478
00:29:54,530 --> 00:29:56,001
It's heavy rain.

479
00:29:58,810 --> 00:29:59,961
Gu Yi,

480
00:30:00,490 --> 00:30:01,921
hold this.

481
00:30:04,330 --> 00:30:06,249
No need. I'm not that weak.

482
00:30:06,250 --> 00:30:06,930
Don't put that on me.

483
00:30:06,931 --> 00:30:08,921
It's the time of times.

484
00:30:08,931 --> 00:30:11,400
You don't want to get sick
and lose to Penny, do you?

485
00:30:12,411 --> 00:30:13,441
True, though.

486
00:30:13,971 --> 00:30:16,569
- Hold it yourself.
- I'm holding the umbrella for you.

487
00:30:16,570 --> 00:30:17,961
Take it.

488
00:31:09,651 --> 00:31:11,040
Santa Claus,

489
00:31:11,131 --> 00:31:13,001
time is almost up.

490
00:31:13,290 --> 00:31:14,970
Even if you don't speak,

491
00:31:14,971 --> 00:31:17,120
I'll charge you.

492
00:31:21,010 --> 00:31:22,560
Gu Yi went on a blind date.

493
00:31:23,731 --> 00:31:24,840
That's normal.

494
00:31:24,931 --> 00:31:26,800
Humans have emotional needs.

495
00:31:27,010 --> 00:31:28,329
Is that

496
00:31:28,330 --> 00:31:29,961
bothering you?

497
00:31:30,570 --> 00:31:31,761
I'm uncomfortable.

498
00:31:32,211 --> 00:31:33,681
Uncomfortable?

499
00:31:34,451 --> 00:31:36,840
Is it because she went on a blind date

500
00:31:36,850 --> 00:31:38,210
or because her focus

501
00:31:38,211 --> 00:31:39,560
isn't on you?

502
00:31:45,250 --> 00:31:46,800
To be frank,

503
00:31:47,131 --> 00:31:48,210
I'm pretty glad

504
00:31:48,211 --> 00:31:50,040
to see you in this condition.

505
00:31:50,810 --> 00:31:53,241
I think this is the first time

506
00:31:53,371 --> 00:31:56,529
you're speaking of troubles
as an ordinary man, not just as a patient,

507
00:31:56,530 --> 00:31:59,360
after all these consultations.

508
00:32:00,330 --> 00:32:02,761
Actually, as for why
you're uncomfortable,

509
00:32:03,131 --> 00:32:05,201
you know the answer.

510
00:32:08,090 --> 00:32:09,400
It's simple.

511
00:32:09,731 --> 00:32:12,329
Your body realizes your emotions

512
00:32:12,330 --> 00:32:13,921
before your brain does.

513
00:32:13,931 --> 00:32:16,001
You're jealous.

514
00:32:21,211 --> 00:32:22,320
I'm jealous

515
00:32:23,090 --> 00:32:24,560
because of Gu Yi?

516
00:32:26,010 --> 00:32:27,690
You're well aware

517
00:32:27,691 --> 00:32:29,040
of how Gu Yi feels about you.

518
00:32:29,651 --> 00:32:31,089
You'll have to

519
00:32:31,090 --> 00:32:33,040
talk this through one day.

520
00:32:34,691 --> 00:32:35,849
Given your personality,

521
00:32:35,850 --> 00:32:36,970
once you do,

522
00:32:36,971 --> 00:32:38,800
both of you are done.

523
00:32:39,211 --> 00:32:41,809
Waiting for someone else's
feelings to disappear

524
00:32:41,810 --> 00:32:43,921
isn't hard for you.

525
00:32:44,770 --> 00:32:46,210
But do you know?

526
00:32:46,211 --> 00:32:48,529
Feelings won't just go away,

527
00:32:48,530 --> 00:32:49,880
they transfer.

528
00:32:50,411 --> 00:32:54,450
Jealousy is a sign from your body

529
00:32:54,451 --> 00:32:57,001
telling you don't want
this relationship to disappear.

530
00:33:02,371 --> 00:33:03,640
She taught me

531
00:33:04,250 --> 00:33:05,880
that when I have emotions,

532
00:33:07,090 --> 00:33:09,001
I can describe them with a metaphor.

533
00:33:09,891 --> 00:33:11,441
I didn't get it at first.

534
00:33:21,731 --> 00:33:23,880
But when I saw her leaving
with another man

535
00:33:25,171 --> 00:33:27,201
at the office,

536
00:33:33,290 --> 00:33:34,800
I suddenly

537
00:33:37,131 --> 00:33:38,360
have this feeling.

538
00:33:41,850 --> 00:33:43,761
It's like someone taking

539
00:33:43,891 --> 00:33:45,721
the apple I was going to buy.

540
00:33:52,451 --> 00:33:53,640
That's a good one.

541
00:33:53,850 --> 00:33:54,921
I got it.

542
00:33:56,490 --> 00:33:57,489
Listen,

543
00:33:57,490 --> 00:33:59,849
we have two options now.

544
00:33:59,850 --> 00:34:00,681
First,

545
00:34:01,290 --> 00:34:04,849
take the apple and go to her.

546
00:34:04,850 --> 00:34:07,289
Follow your heart for once

547
00:34:07,290 --> 00:34:08,721
and see what happens.

548
00:34:09,290 --> 00:34:10,201
Second,

549
00:34:10,571 --> 00:34:12,800
we'll sit on the sofa

550
00:34:12,890 --> 00:34:14,320
and share the apple

551
00:34:14,611 --> 00:34:16,929
without trying anything
outside the plan.

552
00:34:16,930 --> 00:34:18,530
Then, you go home, take the painkiller,

553
00:34:18,531 --> 00:34:19,761
and go straight to bed.

554
00:34:20,131 --> 00:34:21,570
Pretend you feel nothing

555
00:34:21,571 --> 00:34:23,041
today.

556
00:34:37,370 --> 00:34:39,721
You didn't approve of me
stepping into a relationship.

557
00:34:40,691 --> 00:34:42,201
It's not that I look down on you.

558
00:34:42,651 --> 00:34:45,440
You still have a long way to go

559
00:34:45,491 --> 00:34:46,721
before entering one.

560
00:34:47,770 --> 00:34:49,000
Go ahead.

561
00:35:15,171 --> 00:35:16,400
Liang Daiwen?

562
00:35:18,651 --> 00:35:20,161
I'm Gu Yi's colleague.

563
00:35:20,211 --> 00:35:21,641
